    FileSelectorController
    Handle the logic of selecting a file for an import or an export.
    HomeController
    This is the main window of our application and therefore have access to the listeners of every other windows of the application that is callable from the home controller.
    ImportExportController
    Handle the logic of import and export of a project This class is the listener of the ImportExportViewController.ViewListener.
    LoginController
    Handle the logic of the login of a user This class is the listener of the LoginViewController.ViewListener.
    RegisterController
    Handle the logic of registering a user.
    StatisticProjectController
    Handle the logic to show statistics for the projects of a user This class is the listener of the StatisticProjectViewController.ViewListener.
    TaskController
    Handle all the logic related to tasks This class is the listener of the TaskViewController.ViewListener.
    VersionController
    Handle the logic of the versioning of a project This class is the listener of the VersionViewController.ViewListener.

    This class is the listener of the WelcomeViewController.ViewListener.
